  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>When you reach 3rd level</strong></span>, you can program your omni-tool to transform omni-gel into grenades. Choose two grenades from the grenade list. As an action, you can spend 1 omni-gel to create and use a grenade of that type. The Mark of the grenade you create is equal to your soldier level divided by 3 (rounded down).</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">You can spend 8 hours of programming to exchange a selected grenade with a different one.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>At 15th level</strong></span>, you can have 4 grenades programmed into your Omni-tool at once.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">In addition, you can create a grenade with this ability as a bonus action and you can use a grenade as an attack action.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">&nbsp;</p>",
